HEADWORD: Varvel
<hw>Var"vel</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>vervelle</ets>.]</ety> <def>In falconry, one of the rings secured
to the ends of the jesses.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>vervel</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

